Description: Afid Therapeutics, Inc. develops chemical and biochemical technologies and strategies.
Full Description: Afid Therapeutics, Inc. develops chemical and biochemical technologies and strategies that are used in the design, discovery, delivery, and development of new drugs. Its products include lactones and esters acids, hydroxy cyclopentane carboxylic acids and derivatives, hydroxy cyclopentane acetic acids and derivatives, amino acids, cyclopentane amino alcohols, cyclopentanones, bicyclic amines and advanced diamines, amino alcohols and diols, unprotected amino diols, diamines, and oxathiolanes and oxazolidinones. The company also involves in the development of a platform of chiral chemical entities to emulate structural, reactive, and physicochemical aspects of biomolecules that potentiate and direct the chemistry of life processes. In addition, it offers ring systems in various screening collections, which include piperazines, oxazolines, oxazolidinones, morpholines, pyrrolidines, pyrrolidones, aza-sugars, macrolides, lactones, lactams, thiolactams, cyclopentanes, furans, pyrans, quinolines, isoquinolines, quinolones, purines, pyridines, pyrimidines, imidazoles, benzimidazoles, triazoles plus many more. Other functionalities include sulfonamides, phosphates, phosphonates, sulfates, sulfonates, alcohols, acids, amines, and oximes, as well as carbohydrate derivatives, nucleoside analogs, and oligosaccharides. The company’s technology base utilizes the structural richness of carbohydrates to allow intervention and therapies across a range of disease spectrum, including bacterial and viral infections, cancer, autoimmune disorders, cardiovascular disorders, diabetes, and Alzheimer's and other neurological disorders. Its drug targets include kinases, phosphatases, nucleases, glycosidases, glycosyltransferases, ribosomes, cell membranes, and nucleic acids. The company was founded in 2003 and is based in Lansing, Michigan.
Industry Groups: Biotechnology, Health Care, Science and Engineering

Description: Ions are everywhere in nature and ions are responsible for diverse phenomena from the Earth's ionosphere to the luminescence of the Sun.

Full Description: Ions are everywhere in nature and ions are responsible for diverse phenomena from the Earth's ionosphere to the luminescence of the Sun. Ions can be chemically or non-chemically prepared using various ion sources generally involving high voltage or high temperature. These ions are used in a multitude of devices such as water ionizers, mass spectrometers, optical emission spectrometers, particle accelerators, ion implanters, and ion engines. As reactive charged particles, they are also used in air purification by disrupting microbes, and in household items such as smoke detectors and water purifiers. We are in process of developing breakthrough technology to apply ion measuring technology to obtain a signature no measure a variety of things. This technology will have a wide range of commercial applications in many of the world’s multi-billion dollar industries.

Description: Effective Connect
Adim8 LLC develops a unique advertising platform (known as Icon Advertising) for a wide variety of digital systems.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Los Angeles Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Adim8 LLC develops a unique advertising platform (known as Icon Advertising) for a wide variety of digital systems (including mobile phones, tablets, PC, game machines, DVD players, smart TV, etc.) Icon Advertising is a simple concept wherein an application's standard waiting indicator and/or loading bar is replaced with an animated logo, icon etc. which represents a brand or entity. The animation of the logo/icon replaces the functionality of the standard waiting indicator (or loading bar.) This is a form of banner advertising. The significant benefits of Icon Advertising are: * As opposed to many forms of banner ad (which are often ignored or not seen at all) Icon Advertising receives the user's full attention. The user stares at the animation while waiting for the application to load. * Icon Advertising can be entertaining. Waiting events range anywhere from a few seconds to more than 10 seconds. In the hands of creative talent, this time can be converted into entertaining animations that help elevate a company's brand above the digital advertising noise. * Icon Advertising can be highly interactive. In the simplest form, an animation may be clicked in order to open a link. In more complex forms, Icon Advertising can represent an branding campaign with multiple animations and a high level of user interaction. * Icon Advertising does not consume valuable page space. Because it replaces the standard waiting indicator (or loading bar), Icon Advertising is transient. The advertisement disappears when the waiting period is over. However. Icon Advertising includes parameters which allow the application developer to extend the time which the animation is displayed, resulting in increased exposure. * Icon Advertising is perfect for branding activity * Icon Advertising is covered by two (2) patents which apply to the use of animated logo/icon to replace the standard waiting indicator and/or loading bar.

Description: Emerald City Beer Company (ECB) is fanatical about creating the Seattle Lager—a style, culture and taste that is Seattle beer.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Seattle Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Emerald City Beer Company (ECB) is fanatical about creating the Seattle Lager—a style, culture and taste that is Seattle beer.  Across America, the craft beer industry is flourishing!  Washington State, most notably Seattle, is a top 5 craft beer market  that is under supplied with local lagers, ranking 11th as a state in breweries per capita. Most beer served in the US today is a lager style, pilsner, however, most craft beer is focused on ale styles.  Ales are a flavorful and bold contrast to lagers, but are certainly not intended to be crisp & easy drinking like pilsners. ECB makes craft lager beer for those who want it all, flavorful & easy drinking! ECB primarily targets the young and social crowd, individuals with an active social life, and often stressful professional life, who frequent a wide range of venues for entertainment including, restaurants, bars, sporting events, concerts, outdoor activities and various community events.  ECB has some exciting goals for the next year! We currently offer a year-around lager, and two of four planned seasonal lagers. Our year-around lager is the only style available today in 16oz aluminum cans. The plan for the next year is to release the final two seasonal lagers and put all four of the seasonal lagers into cans. We'll then release a variety pack of ten 16oz cans that includes all five different beers styles and 4-packs of the individual style when in season. ECB currently contracts the large production batches of beer with another local craft brewery in Western Washington. This allows ECB to better focus resources on building demand for our beers, instead of investing in supply assets that make them. In the next five years, we aspire to reach 15k barrels of annual production, qualifying us a regional craft-brewery. At these production volumes, it'll make sense for ECB to either sell it's brands to a larger brewer, or to build-in it's own facility, so to recapture the production margin for our investors.

Description: Onedepth is cloud storage software that automatically retrieves, uploads, organizes and saves entire search sessions on the cloud.
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Onedepth is cloud storage for search. The software automatically retrieves, uploads, organizes and saves entire search sessions on the cloud. Users can then access these search sessions on any device.  With a mixture of intrigue, frustration, and awe for the power of information in our day and age, the founders of Onedepth, Alex Park and Thomas Arthur, sought out ways in which they could help make search, the gateway for online information, more of an experience than a task.  Realizing that search was outdated in many ways, having had no major innovations within the past decade, the founders of Onedepth decided to place emphasis on post-query navigation, or the phase in which people are actually spending the majority of their time, sifting through content to ultimately make decisions, discover, or create something of value.  Feeling that search data was just as important as individual files, the founders of Onedepth aimed to create a service that helped users store their search data and truly navigate through it while not having to manually clip, copy, save or print individual web content.  Onedepth is currently in Beta.
Industry Groups: Administrative Services, Artificial Intelligence (AI), Data and Analytics, Information Technology, Internet Services, Other, Software, Transportation

Headquarters Regions: Greater Atlanta Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: The Garden’s Executive Club, Inc., founded by Ebony Ormond-Ham, is planting its first power seed in the vintage tourism attractions of downtown Stone Mountain; within a 2 mile radius of Stone Mountain Park’s West Gate entrance. A 2-story, 6,000-square-foot, 2acre, tribute to female executives. Any entrepreneur or C-suite executive will tell you, leading a team can be as rewarding as it is punishing, with the long hours, cash-flow woes, and expectations to meet your customers and employees highest demands. Imagine an elite club of executive female powerhouses finally able to debunk the stigma that “It’s lonely at the top”. The Garden’s Executive Club will offer private executive coaching, mental health support groups, counseling, access to angel investors, private lenders, grant research, and so much more! While men have long enjoyed support from networks and clubs that cater to them, women historically have had fewer options–particularly when they’re younger. No Worries! It’s Our Time and It’s Our Turn. We’re getting ready to change this narrative for good by offering C-suite execs and rising vice presidents, mentorship opportunities across various industries, focused career coaching sessions, and networking events. There’s also access to a clubhouse, a speaker series, a book club, and a host of workshops and professional development trainings ahead of us. Tier 1 C-Suite Elite execs will have to already be working in high-level jobs as CEO’s, Presidents or VP’s, overseeing entrepreneurial endeavors with yearly gross revenues of $75k or seeking to dominate in top thriving industries such as Healthcare, Childcare, IT TECH, Oil, Construction, Real Estate or Finance. “The worst place to find yourself is climbing a ladder with nowhere to go and no one to catch you, should you fall, said, Garden of OH’s founding Exec, Ebony OH.
